st", "module" "magatama.cells.shionome_social_post", "murakumoNode" "naphtali", "phase" "periodic (event)", "io" "aggregate finding → dry-run networkPost (member-signed, mirror disclaimer, no-trade body scan, ≥2 sources); live post Council Lv6+ + operator gated"}], "descriptionJa" "潮目 (shionome) — クロスアセットの資金フロー観測所。公開市場データ(取引所データ・資金フローレポート・中央銀行公表・オンチェーン暗号資産・指数プロバイダ)を ingest し、世界の資金を公的な器(資産クラス/セクター/地域/テーマ)のグラフとしてモデル化、観測された資金移動 — 器ごとの純流入(どこに資金が向かっているか)・回転ペア(どこからどこへ)・流入集中度(HHI)・クロスアセットのレジーム記述(リスクオン/オフ/まちまち) — を一つの kotoba Datom フローグラフに編み、集計所見を dry-run social post として narrate する。最重要不変条件は トレードはしない(G2): 売買シグナル・目標価格・オーバー/アンダーウェイト・ポジション提案を一切出さない — trade/advisory トークンは flow・bucket・post body 上で構造的に表現不能で、全出力に noTradeNotice=true。観測ミラー(G5)であってシグナルではない。集計・edge-primary(G4)で個別の器に格付け/スコアを持たない。出典必須(G3, フローごとに ≥2 公開出典)。no-doxxing(G1/G9 — 器は公的な資産カテゴリで、個人・口座・ポートフォリオではない)。no-server-key(G7)+ outward-gated(G8): live market-data ingest と live posting は Council Lv6+ + operator + 本人署名 gated。R0 は設計 + offline analyzer + dry-run posts + append-only kotoba Datom log に content-addressed トランザクションを永続化する自律ハートビートループ(live 外部 I/O は gated のまま)。", "tier" "Tier-B", "primaryLexicon" "com.etzhayyim.shionome.capitalFlowObservation", "glyph" "潮目", "@type" "ActorManifest", "nonGoals" {"N1" "NOT a trading system / signal service / robo-advisor (トレードはしない — no broker, no order book, no execution, no buy/sell signal, no price target)", "N2" "NOT investment advice or a recommendation engine (non-advisory; informational mirror only)", "N3" "NOT a per-asset rating / score / ranking-to-buy", "N4" "NOT a surveillance system of individual investors / accounts / portfolios (public market aggregates only; no-doxxing)", "N5" "NOT a commercial market-data terminal (Bloomberg / Refinitiv / FactSet / CapIQ / 四季報 prohibited as source)", "N6" "NOT a forecaster (mitooshi owns probabilistic forecasts; shionome observes realized flows)", "N7" "NOT a RisingWave / SQL / Datomic store — kotoba Datom log only"}, "description" "潮目 (shionome) — a cross-asset capital-flow observatory. It ingests PUBLIC market data (exchange data, fund-flow reports, central-bank releases, on-chain crypto, index providers), models the world's capital as a graph of public BUCKETS (asset-class / sector / region / theme), and weaves OBSERVED capital movement — net flow per bucket (where money is going/leaving), rotation pairs (どこからどこへ), inflow concentration (HHI), and a FACTUAL cross-asset regime descriptor (risk-on/off/mixed) — then narrates aggregate findings as DRY-RUN social posts. THE DEFINING INVARIANT is トレードはしない (G2 no-trade): shionome NEVER emits a buy/sell signal, a price target, an over/under-weight call, or a portfolio instruction — trade/advisory tokens are structurally unrepresentable on flows, buckets, and post bodies, and every output carries noTradeNotice=true. An observational MIRROR (G5), never a trade signal; aggregate + edge-primary (G4) with no per-bucket rating/score; sourced (G3, ≥2 public-source citations per flow); no-doxxing (G1/G9 — buckets are public asset categories, never persons/accounts/portfolios). no-server-key (G7) + outward-gated (G8): live market-data ingest + live posting are Council Lv6+ + operator + member-signature gated; R0 = design + offline analyzer + dry-run posts + an AUTONOMOUS heartbeat loop that persists content-addressed Datom transactions to the append-only kotoba Datom log (live external I/O stays gated).", "purpose" "Ingests PUBLIC market data across asset classes (equities / govt-bonds / credit / commodities / FX / crypto / real-estate / cash) and weaves OBSERVED capital rotation — どこからどこへ資金が流れているか — into one kotoba Datom flow-graph + dry-run social posts. Observational mirror of where money MOVED; NEVER trades, never a buy/sell signal, never a price target (トレードはしない). Aggregate-first, edge-primary, non-advisory."}}
